25static inline isc_result_t
26fromtext_ch_a(ARGS_FROMTEXT) {
27 isc_token_t token;
28 dns_name_t name;
29 isc_buffer_t buffer;
30
31 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_a);
32 REQUIRE(rdclass == dns_rdataclass_ch); /* 3 */
33
34 UNUSED(type);
35 UNUSED(callbacks);
36
37 RETERR(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token, isc_tokentype_string,
38 false));
39
40 /* get domain name */
41 dns_name_init(&name, NULL);
42 buffer_fromregion(&buffer, &token.value.as_region);
43 if (origin == NULL)
44 origin = dns_rootname;
45 RETTOK(dns_name_fromtext(&name, &buffer, origin, options, target));
46 if ((options & DNS_RDATA_CHECKNAMES) != 0 &&
47 (options & DNS_RDATA_CHECKREVERSE) != 0) {
48 bool ok;
49 ok = dns_name_ishostname(&name, false);
50 if (!ok && (options & DNS_RDATA_CHECKNAMESFAIL) != 0)
51 RETTOK(DNS_R_BADNAME);
52 if (!ok && callbacks != NULL)
53 warn_badname(&name, lexer, callbacks);
54 }
55
56 /* 16-bit octal address */
57 RETERR(isc_lex_getoctaltoken(lexer, &token, false));
58 if (token.value.as_ulong > 0xffffU)
59 RETTOK(ISC_R_RANGE);
60 return (uint16_tobuffer(token.value.as_ulong, target));
61}
62
63static inline isc_result_t
64totext_ch_a(ARGS_TOTEXT) {
65 isc_region_t region;
66 dns_name_t name;
67 dns_name_t prefix;
68 bool sub;
69 char buf[sizeof("0177777")];
70 uint16_t addr;
71
72 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_a);
73 REQUIRE(rdata->rdclass == dns_rdataclass_ch); /* 3 */
74 REQUIRE(rdata->length != 0);
75
76 dns_name_init(&name, NULL);
77 dns_name_init(&prefix, NULL);
78
79 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &region);
80 dns_name_fromregion(&name, &region);
81 isc_region_consume(&region, name_length(&name));
82 addr = uint16_fromregion(&region);
83
84 sub = name_prefix(&name, tctx->origin, &prefix);
85 RETERR(dns_name_totext(&prefix, sub, target));
86
87 snprintf(buf, sizeof(buf), "%o", addr); /* note octal */
88 RETERR(str_totext(" ", target));
89 return (str_totext(buf, target));
90}
91
92static inline isc_result_t
93fromwire_ch_a(ARGS_FROMWIRE) {
94 isc_region_t sregion;
95 isc_region_t tregion;
96 dns_name_t name;
97
98 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_a);
99 REQUIRE(rdclass == dns_rdataclass_ch);
100
101 UNUSED(type);
102 UNUSED(rdclass);
103
104 dns_decompress_setmethods(dctx, DNS_COMPRESS_GLOBAL14);
105
106 dns_name_init(&name, NULL);
107
108 RETERR(dns_name_fromwire(&name, source, dctx, options, target));
109
110 isc_buffer_activeregion(source, &sregion);
111 isc_buffer_availableregion(target, &tregion);
112 if (sregion.length < 2)
113 return (ISC_R_UNEXPECTEDEND);
114 if (tregion.length < 2)
115 return (ISC_R_NOSPACE);
116
117 memmove(tregion.base, sregion.base, 2);
118 isc_buffer_forward(source, 2);
119 isc_buffer_add(target, 2);
120
121 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
122}
123
124static inline isc_result_t
125towire_ch_a(ARGS_TOWIRE) {
126 dns_name_t name;
127 dns_offsets_t offsets;
128 isc_region_t sregion;
129 isc_region_t tregion;
130
131 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_a);
132 REQUIRE(rdata->rdclass == dns_rdataclass_ch);
133 REQUIRE(rdata->length != 0);
134
135 dns_compress_setmethods(cctx, DNS_COMPRESS_GLOBAL14);
136
137 dns_name_init(&name, offsets);
138
139 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &sregion);
140
141 dns_name_fromregion(&name, &sregion);
142 isc_region_consume(&sregion, name_length(&name));
143 RETERR(dns_name_towire(&name, cctx, target));
144
145 isc_buffer_availableregion(target, &tregion);
146 if (tregion.length < 2)
147 return (ISC_R_NOSPACE);
148
149 memmove(tregion.base, sregion.base, 2);
150 isc_buffer_add(target, 2);
151 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
152}

154static inline int
155compare_ch_a(ARGS_COMPARE) {
156 dns_name_t name1;
157 dns_name_t name2;
158 isc_region_t region1;
159 isc_region_t region2;
160 int order;
161
162 REQUIRE(rdata1->type == rdata2->type);
163 REQUIRE(rdata1->rdclass == rdata2->rdclass);
164 REQUIRE(rdata1->type == dns_rdatatype_a);
165 REQUIRE(rdata1->rdclass == dns_rdataclass_ch);
166 REQUIRE(rdata1->length != 0);
167 REQUIRE(rdata2->length != 0);
168
169 dns_name_init(&name1, NULL);
170 dns_name_init(&name2, NULL);
171
172 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata1, &region1);
173 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata2, &region2);
174
175 dns_name_fromregion(&name1, &region1);
176 dns_name_fromregion(&name2, &region2);
177 isc_region_consume(&region1, name_length(&name1));
178 isc_region_consume(&region2, name_length(&name2));
179
180 order = dns_name_rdatacompare(&name1, &name2);
181 if (order != 0)
182 return (order);
183
184 order = memcmp(region1.base, region2.base, 2);
185 if (order != 0)
186 order = (order < 0) ? -1 : 1;
187 return (order);
188}

190static inline isc_result_t
191fromstruct_ch_a(ARGS_FROMSTRUCT) {
192 dns_rdata_ch_a_t *a = source;
193 isc_region_t region;
194
195 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_a);
196 REQUIRE(source != NULL);
197 REQUIRE(a->common.rdtype == type);
198 REQUIRE(a->common.rdclass == rdclass);
199
200 UNUSED(type);
201 UNUSED(rdclass);
202
203 dns_name_toregion(&a->ch_addr_dom, &region);
204 RETERR(isc_buffer_copyregion(target, &region));
205
206 return (uint16_tobuffer(ntohs(a->ch_addr), target));
207}
208
209static inline isc_result_t
210tostruct_ch_a(ARGS_TOSTRUCT) {
211 dns_rdata_ch_a_t *a = target;
212 isc_region_t region;
213 dns_name_t name;
214
215 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_a);
216 REQUIRE(rdata->rdclass == dns_rdataclass_ch);
217 REQUIRE(rdata->length != 0);
218
219 a->common.rdclass = rdata->rdclass;
220 a->common.rdtype = rdata->type;
221 ISC_LINK_INIT(&a->common, link);
222
223 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &region);
224
225 dns_name_init(&name, NULL);
226 dns_name_fromregion(&name, &region);
227 isc_region_consume(&region, name_length(&name));
228
229 dns_name_init(&a->ch_addr_dom, NULL);
230 RETERR(name_duporclone(&name, mctx, &a->ch_addr_dom));
231 a->ch_addr = htons(uint16_fromregion(&region));
232 a->mctx = mctx;
233 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
234}
235
236static inline void
237freestruct_ch_a(ARGS_FREESTRUCT) {
238 dns_rdata_ch_a_t *a = source;
239
240 REQUIRE(source != NULL);
241 REQUIRE(a->common.rdtype == dns_rdatatype_a);
242
243 if (a->mctx == NULL)
244 return;
245
246 dns_name_free(&a->ch_addr_dom, a->mctx);
247 a->mctx = NULL;
248}

251additionaldata_ch_a(ARGS_ADDLDATA) {
252
253 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_a);
254 REQUIRE(rdata->rdclass == dns_rdataclass_ch);
255
256 UNUSED(rdata);
257 UNUSED(add);
258 UNUSED(arg);
259
260 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);

263static inline isc_result_t
264digest_ch_a(ARGS_DIGEST) {
265 isc_region_t r;
266 dns_name_t name;
267
268 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_a);
269 REQUIRE(rdata->rdclass == dns_rdataclass_ch);
270
271 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &r);
272 dns_name_init(&name, NULL);
273 dns_name_fromregion(&name, &r);
274 isc_region_consume(&r, name_length(&name));
275 RETERR(dns_name_digest(&name, digest, arg));
276 return ((digest)(arg, &r));
277}

279static inline bool
280checkowner_ch_a(ARGS_CHECKOWNER) {
281
282 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_a);
283 REQUIRE(rdclass == dns_rdataclass_ch);
284
285 UNUSED(type);
286
287 return (dns_name_ishostname(name, wildcard));
288}
289
290static inline bool
291checknames_ch_a(ARGS_CHECKNAMES) {
292 isc_region_t region;
293 dns_name_t name;
294
295 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_a);
296 REQUIRE(rdata->rdclass == dns_rdataclass_ch);
297
298 UNUSED(owner);
299
300 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &region);
301 dns_name_init(&name, NULL);
302 dns_name_fromregion(&name, &region);
303 if (!dns_name_ishostname(&name, false)) {
304 if (bad != NULL)
305 dns_name_clone(&name, bad);
306 return (false);
307 }
308
309 return (true);
310}
311
312static inline int
313casecompare_ch_a(ARGS_COMPARE) {
314 return (compare_ch_a(rdata1, rdata2));
315}
